S.FORM: Austria Gaga kska Owcow ka Austria, 47 20 N, 13 20 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 83,871 sq km(hangan na o Tg114) (knlbanga dxgal o 82,445 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 1,426 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 8,711,770 hiyi. Gaga Vienna ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 26 idas 10 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Austria ga wada sugan 38.40 ka dxgal qpahan, 47.20 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 14.40 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Alexander Van der Bellen, pnaah hngkawas2017 idas 1 jiyax 26pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
